OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fand overnight will see a mixture of
OL,7,Fsunny then clear spells and a few
OL,8,Fpassing showers. Winds a moderate to
OL,9,Ffresh southwesterly veering westerly.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FBright or sunny spells and
OL,12,Fsome showers through the day, perhaps
OL,13,Fa bit more persistent in the evening.
OL,14,FLight to moderate breeze. Colder.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloud
OL,17,Fand showery rain to start on Sunday,
OL,18,Fthen bright spells and showers,
OL,19,Fperhaps wintry over Shetland. Drier
OL,20,Fand brighter on Monday then showery
OL,21,Fand breezy on Tuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
